A tribute to MaxCapacity DOS-Punk that I couldn't have. I Felt in love with a DOS-punk and did all I could to collect it but failed.

A painting re-designing and re-interpretating this cool project of MaxCapacity. Also, a tribute to him and his lovely glitchy artworks.
